data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
-Collect your evidence files into one folder. Click "Select Directory" button and select this folder.
-You need to have a hosting account which can run php scripts (you can register for a free one) Open bust.php with text editor. Change password section, save it. Upload both bust.php and command.txt files to your website. Paste your command.txt's url to url section (http://yourwebsite.com/command.txt) You can check it if it's available with "check it" button
-Fill the other settings fields
-Press "Save Settings" button
-When you click "Connect" button, the program starts to check command.txt file for every 60seconds. If you give the command, program will start to wipe your target folder.
-When you click "Connect" button the program will be still checking for the command even pc is restarted. If you want't to cancel the process, click "Disconnect" button
-If you want to change settings, click "Disconnect" button first -You can wipe your folder via "Wipe Them Now" button manually
*Giving Wipe Command* -Open (http://yourwebsite.com/bust.php) with your mobile phone's or computer's browser -Enter your password (wiping starts)
